## PRODUCT_DB Rule\
\
`PRODUCT_DB` is locked.\
\
No agent may modify `PRODUCT_DB` in any form without explicit approval.\
\
This includes:\
\
- PDF extracted data\
- web extracted data\
- AI generated data\
- manually entered data\
- demo/sample data\
- cleanup\
- normalization\
- schema changes\
- small corrections\
\
All new product data must first go through staging, review and approval.\
