## Do Not Do Yet\
\
Do not start with:\
\
- mass PDF ingestion\
- live web scraping\
- Supabase migration\
- marketplace/cart features\
- pricing/payment features\
- major redesign\
- PRODUCT_DB expansion\
- deployment\
\
These come later.\
\
## Final Principle\
\
ToolAdvisor must be built through controlled, auditable, agent-driven execution.\
\
The system must prevent uncontrolled changes, not depend on memory, and keep every decision traceable through repo files, tasks, worklog and GitHub Actions.}